  "texts": [
    "For instance, Llama3 has low average TREC sensitivity with the 1-shot strategy, but there are a non-negligible number of samples for which sensitivity is still very high.",
    "If a developer does not have access to ground truth labels at all, these samples can be manually inspected or given to labelers to identify situations that need special care.",
    "As a result, the labeling cost is reduced and the developer knows how to improve the prompt.",
    "In Appendix B, we demonstrate how to adjust prompts according to most sensitive samples, which reduces sensitivity and improves classification accuracy.",
    "When some ground truth information is available, Figure 3 Bottom: we plot the sensitivity S τ for each class and prompting strategy (Llama3)."
